data.description: Charming bungalow in the heart of Springfield! Just minutes from downtown shopping, dining and activities, this 3BR, 2BA home has been remodeled top to bottom within the past 3 years. A covered front porch spans the width of the house, perfect for warm spring nights. At the entry, luxury vinyl plank floors flow through the living area, into the kitchen, which features gleaming stainless appliances, modern cabinetry and neutral tile floors. A live edge eat-in bar separates the kitchen from living quarters. Huge dining area is perfect for entertaing! Master, with en suite bath, hosts a marble tile surround in the shower. Fresh vanity features a white on white color scheme. The additional hall bathroom boasts a large shower and modern vanity. Detached garage features a workshop or additional storage area above the back stall. New additions include additional insulation in the attic, new concrete patio and a fully fenced backyard, with a 20-ft rolling gate, 12-ft swing gate and a 6-ft swing gate, so all your 'toys' are accessible and secure! See this one before it's GONE!
